column16: Laynce Nix grounds out sharply to first baseman Jack Hannahan.
Ben Revere grounds out, shortstop Zack Cozart to first baseman Jack Hannahan.
Freddy Galvis homers (1) on a line drive to right field.    John Mayberry scores.
Erik Kratz flies out to right fielder Jay Bruce.   John Mayberry to 3rd.
John Mayberry doubles (4) on a sharp line drive to left fielder Chris Heisey.
